  <brief_title>Pilot Trial of &quot;Chemo-Switch&quot; Regimen to Treat Advanced Melanoma</brief_title>
  <official_title>Phase II Pilot Trial of &quot;Chemo-Switch&quot; Regimen of Biochemotherapy Followed by Daily Low-Dose Temozolomide Plus Sorafenib in Advanced Melanoma</official_title>
